                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="center">II. COSTA RICA</p>
                <p>For documentation on the Costa Rican presidential election, civil war, and
                    invasion by armed forces from Nicaragua, and United States participation in
                    bilateral and multilateral remedial measures, see <ref target="#pg_488">pages
                        488</ref> ff. With particular reference to the question of recognition of
                    the Costa Rican regime, see telegram 117, May 3, 1948, 6 p. m. to the Embassy in
                    Costa Rica, and memorandum of telephone conversation by Mr. Woodward, June 22,
                    1948, <ref target="#pg_525">pages 525</ref> and <ref target="#pg_529">529</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
